### Day 16 - HubSpot Deal and Association API Pattern
# Use with VS Code REST Client or similar tools.
# Replace {{HUBSPOT_PRIVATE_APP_TOKEN}} locally only.
# Do not commit real tokens.

### Search deal by custom dedupe key
POST https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v3/objects/deals/search
Authorization: Bearer {{HUBSPOT_PRIVATE_APP_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filterGroups": [
    {
      "filters": [
        {
          "propertyName": "ve_deal_dedupe_key",
          "operator": "EQ",
          "value": "external_id:opp-2001"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "properties": ["dealname", "amount", "dealstage", "pipeline", "closedate", "ve_deal_dedupe_key"],
  "limit": 1
}

### Create deal if not found
POST https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v3/objects/deals
Authorization: Bearer {{HUBSPOT_PRIVATE_APP_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "properties": {
    "dealname": "Meridian Rail - Licence Optimisation Pilot",
    "amount": "12000",
    "dealstage": "appointmentscheduled",
    "pipeline": "default",
    "closedate": "2026-07-31",
    "deal_currency_code": "GBP",
    "ve_external_opportunity_id": "OPP-2001",
    "ve_deal_dedupe_key": "external_id:opp-2001"
  }
}

### Update deal if found
PATCH https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v3/objects/deals/{{DEAL_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{HUBSPOT_PRIVATE_APP_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "properties": {
    "amount": "15000",
    "dealstage": "presentationscheduled",
    "closedate": "2026-08-10"
  }
}

### Associate contact to company
PUT https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v4/objects/contacts/{{CONTACT_ID}}/associations/default/companies/{{COMPANY_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{HUBSPOT_PRIVATE_APP_TOKEN}}

### Associate deal to company
PUT https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v4/objects/deals/{{DEAL_ID}}/associations/default/companies/{{COMPANY_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{HUBSPOT_PRIVATE_APP_TOKEN}}

### Associate deal to contact
PUT https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v4/objects/deals/{{DEAL_ID}}/associations/default/contacts/{{CONTACT_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{HUBSPOT_PRIVATE_APP_TOKEN}}
